_sText:
Map features a Lake, Blue Dungeon (T-SPawn), Castle (CT-Spawn) and 2 Caves. Floating Island and the Cabin in the Woods are not reachable (without cheats). All Assets (Textures/Sounds) are property of ReLogic/Redigit (Creator of Terraria) and are used with Permission.
Note:

A seperate Garrys Mod Version is available trough the Garrys Mod Addon Browser or Workshop. The Garrys Mod Version is slightly different hence the filename (fy_terraria_gm) to avoid version mismatches.

Also available for CS:GO in the Workshop
